wow... almost 214 GB.. thanks a lot.

How do i play it? 
I've been downloading for 5 weeks and now to find out i cant play it kinda sucks.. please reply!

Powerdvd no lo reproduce porque falta la subcarpeta AUXDATA, dentro de la carpeta BDMV. Extraer el contenido del ISO en el disco duro y crear la carpeta vacia y listo. 

Powerdvd will not play because there is no AUXDATA subfolder within the BDMV folder. Extract the ISO on your hard disk and create the folder empty and ready.
